<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/discovery-reveals-how-to-prevent-organ-damage-in-pancreatitis/">Discovery reveals how to prevent organ damage in pancreatitis</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
